Israel says they were executed

00:06:30.223 --> 00:06:31.924
in a tunnel in Gaza,

00:06:31.924 --> 00:06:34.894
shot to death at close range.

00:06:35.561 --> 00:06:36.295
According to the Israeli

00:06:36.295 --> 00:06:37.263
prime Minister's office,

00:06:37.263 --> 00:06:39.832
there believed to be about 101 hostages

00:06:39.832 --> 00:06:41.467
still remaining in Gaza,

00:06:41.467 --> 00:06:43.836
35 are believed to be dead.

00:06:43.836 --> 00:06:44.637
Short time ago,

00:06:44.637 --> 00:06:46.873
I spoke with Orna and Ronen Neutra,

00:06:46.873 --> 00:06:48.875
whose son Omer is another

00:06:48.875 --> 00:06:50.042
Israeli American still

00:06:50.042 --> 00:06:50.877
being held captive.

00:06:52.745 --> 00:06:54.280
Orna Ronen, thank you for

00:06:54.280 --> 00:06:55.715
talking with me today.

00:06:55.715 --> 00:06:57.450
I know you consider John

00:06:57.450 --> 00:06:58.451
Poland and Rachel

00:06:58.451 --> 00:07:01.254
Goldberg, Poland family.

00:07:01.254 --> 00:07:04.257
How are you dealing with what's happened?

00:07:05.892 --> 00:07:08.394
We are completely devastated, Anderson.

00:07:08.394 --> 00:07:10.863
This shouldn't have happened.

00:07:10.863 --> 00:07:12.598
Hirsch was supposed to come out

00:07:12.598 --> 00:07:14.700
in the first phase of a deal

00:07:14.700 --> 00:07:16.669
that's been on the table for a long time

00:07:16.669 --> 00:07:19.772
now, and it's just completely outrageous

00:07:19.772 --> 00:07:20.873
and devastating

00:07:20.873 --> 00:07:22.942
that this is what happened.

00:07:22.942 --> 00:07:24.143
Hirsch managed

00:07:24.143 --> 00:07:27.547
to survive in the 11 most terrible months

00:07:28.181 --> 00:07:29.115
with the monsters

00:07:29.115 --> 00:07:31.884
of, of of Hamas in Gaza,

00:07:31.884 --> 00:07:33.786
and yet was murdered

00:07:33.786 --> 00:07:36.088
and executed a couple of days ago

00:07:36.088 --> 00:07:37.323
in a most brutal way.

00:07:37.323 --> 00:07:39.525
It just heartbreaking.

00:07:39.525 --> 00:07:42.528
Rachel, yesterday, at the funeral said,

00:07:43.396 --> 00:07:44.397
that that she hopes

00:07:44.397 --> 00:07:46.532
that that Hirsch's death will be

00:07:46.532 --> 00:07:47.900
what she called a turning point

00:07:47.900 --> 00:07:49.402
in this horrible situation.

00:07:49.402 --> 00:07:52.405
And, and John said maybe, just maybe,

00:07:52.605 --> 00:07:53.573
your death, meaning

00:07:53.573 --> 00:07:55.475
Hirsch's death is the stone,

00:07:55.475 --> 00:07:57.009
the fuel that will bring home

00:07:57.009 --> 00:07:59.712
the remaining 101 hostages.

00:07:59.712 --> 00:08:00.913
Do you think that's possible?

