the compromises

00:08:19.165 --> 00:08:20.399
needed to reach a deal

00:08:20.399 --> 00:08:21.400
to bring our son

00:08:21.400 --> 00:08:23.536
and the other hostages back.

00:08:23.536 --> 00:08:26.005
We sure see, the Israeli

00:08:26.005 --> 00:08:27.940
public pouring in big numbers

